OL,3,CBritain facing a water scarcity
OL,4,Ccrisis. What is being done to prevent
OL,5,Cit?
OL,7,FThe answer is threefold - a changing
OL,8,Fclimate, population growth and aging
OL,9,Finfrastructure are putting the UK at
OL,10,Frisk.
OL,12,FEngland alone faces a shortfall of
OL,13,Ffive billion litres of water a day -
OL,14,Fthat's over two million wheelie bins
OL,15,Ffull of water every day - by 2050,
OL,16,Faccording to figures from the
OL,17,FEnvironment Agency.
