OL,3,CBritain facing a water scarcity
OL,4,Ccrisis. What is being done to prevent
OL,5,Cit?
OL,7,FNo new reservoirs have been built here
OL,8,Fin 30 years. The government has
OL,9,Fannounced plans to build nine, but
OL,10,Fthese will not all be online until the
OL,11,F2040s.
OL,13,FHavant Thickett in Hampshire is the
OL,14,Fonly new reservoir where construction
OL,15,Fis already underway, but it is still
OL,16,Fat least seven years from being
OL,17,Foperational.
