OL,3,CBritain facing a water scarcity
OL,4,Ccrisis. What is being done to prevent
OL,5,Cit?
OL,7,FBob Taylor, CEO of Portsmouth Water,
OL,8,Fthe company behind the new reservoir
OL,9,Fat Havant Thickett told ITV News that
OL,10,Fa combination of climate change and a
OL,11,Flack of infrastructure means we are
OL,12,Flosing water.
OL,14,F"Our whole water infrastructure is
OL,15,Fbuilt around the seasons - so high
OL,16,Frainfall in the winter time that is
OL,17,Fconserved through reservoirs and
OL,18,Fstorage" he said.
