OL,7,FWater storage is not the only solution
OL,8,Fto the shortfall the nation is facing.
OL,10,FEven when all the new reservoirs are
OL,11,Fup and running, they will only make up
OL,12,Fa third of the predicted deficit.
OL,14,FOther savings will need to come from
OL,15,Ffixing leakages, moving water and
OL,16,Fimproving water efficiency.
